The paper discusses deep neural networks and their application in computer vision, which suggests that it belongs to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also focuses on improving the efficiency of sparse convolutional neural networks on GPUs, which suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
